etahn-abaht-commander-new-republic-legen.ability:
While a friendly ship is defending, during the Spend Defense Tokens step, it may discard a :brace: defense token to resolve that token's effect.
While a friendly ship or squadron resolves the :brace: defense effect, if it is at distance 1-3 of another friendly ship, it reduces the total damage to half rounded down, to a minimum of 1.
